(362, 'Science', 'Psychedelic Simulation Studies Real Sun’s Magnetic Field | Video', '"http://www.space.com/images/i/000/054/314/original/SP_160324_solar_plasma_motion.jpg?interpolation=lanczos-none&amp;fit=around|160:100&amp;crop=160:100;*,*"', 'Much of our Sun exists in the ‘fourth state of matter:’ plasma; more energetic than normal gasses. This plasma’s viscosity and turbulence shapes our star’s magnetic field.  ', 'Thu, 24 Mar 2016 11:39:00 EDT', 'http://www.space.com/32365-solar-plasma-motion-simulated-to-study-magnetic-field-video.html'),
